{"tid":263213,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨遊日本] 7日6夜九洲一人之旅","createTime":"2017-05-29T20:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T03:53:10.000Z","uid":62282,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a590aab5f16a2c520f0f781efedc7cd1cfb6713","tid":263213,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T20:32:08.000Z","msg":"利申左先第一次寫遊記<br />\n<br />\nGrad Trip諗住求其去個旅行, 咁啱見到有去程送回程就即刻狗衝去買, 雖然都唔係話好平, 冇加寄艙行李Total HKD800左右<br />\n<br />\n去之前冇乜時間plan行程, <a href=\"http://所以淨係上左booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%B7%A8%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%8A%E5%B7%A6booking.com&d=XgJxA7mL2pmn53RU8UFtOp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b0ee366a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">所以淨係上左booking.com</a>到求其搵左間響福岡嘅Hostel, book左間一人房6晚, 諗住唔洗煩, 點知臨去果陣先發現局住每個地方都要即日來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 福岡<br />\n<br />\n搭Express 下晝1點機, 落機果陣已經係當地 5點幾, 因為唔係住博多, 所以要搭幾程鐵先去到間Hostel嘅附近, 人生路不熟就打開個google map搵路順便睇下附近有啲乜野既鋪頭, 點知行下行下先發現行錯方向, 最後7點半先去到Hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/XnYc5u0lxSjN5r1Pguk1NNFmeIkKP13z/P_20170516_121146_HDR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2FXnYc5u0lxSjN5r1Pguk1NNFmeIkKP13z%2FP_20170516_121146_HDR.jpg&h=c3ce72ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oiqm2rue\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foiqm2rue&h=f2d25d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實間房都唔錯, 有張床有張枱仲有私人廁所, 平均都係百幾蚊港紙一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/n1dFqyYdDzh7YF6LUibnlfjfg24jrT9R/IMG-20170516-WA0007.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2Fn1dFqyYdDzh7YF6LUibnlfjfg24jrT9R%2FIMG-20170516-WA0007.jpg&h=7cdd18ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係房到hea左陣就出去搵野食同探險, 因為小弟唔食生野, 基本上可以揀嘅選擇已經小左一大半, 行左好耐都搵唔到岩食嘅野就買左個熱狗拎返Hostel食, 其實都幾好食, 全部野食都係即炸即整, 之後用我啲垃圾日文問個店主邊到有便利店, 個店主仲親自行出黎帶我行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z2l910ax\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz2l910ax&h=a40f1fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 2 佐賀 諫早<br />\n<br />\n因為琴日太趕冇時間去買JR Pass, 所以第2日要好早起身去博多站買Pass, 因為冇Pass嘅關係, 由Hostel去博多果程JR車錢係要自己比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n響Hostel間房到望出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/N1T8yBwuUQNYid7sblL8V9xDIYAZSgkR/DSC_0003.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2FN1T8yBwuUQNYid7sblL8V9xDIYAZSgkR%2FDSC_0003.JPG&h=130188ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇到啲人話佐賀和牛好好食, 於是就搭火車出發去佐賀<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/53ojwc2v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F53ojwc2v&h=def4a962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到果陣因為太早, 所以就睇下附近有啲咩地方好hea, 見到地圖話附近有神社有美術館博物館, 咁就沿住條大街向前行<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xgdcy528\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxgdcy528&h=1feee1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英式嘅電話亭<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1suw6x3v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1suw6x3v&h=98ca9470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過教堂睇下有冇人唱哈利路亞<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i18eurct\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi18eurct&h=97d9e648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周圍都有好多呢啲小河, 雖然唔臭但係都幾污糟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xfm138ze\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxfm138ze&h=468d3537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活化左啲貨櫃用黎做展覽<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0tg3b6hj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0tg3b6hj&h=23bd466c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐賀市歷史民俗館, 基本上係由幾橦翻新左嘅歷史建築物組成嘅一條街<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wvo21bsm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwvo21bsm&h=a08c1f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fo28hm4k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffo28hm4k&h=8e31d1ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐嘉神社<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s1nq9gby\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs1nq9gby&h=3d830062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b5azj8ic\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb5azj8ic&h=7e52a776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pe0ugqny\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpe0ugqny&h=49d14a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n神社入面居然有啲歷史展覽<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tm9xoepl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftm9xoepl&h=cec65a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有小朋友響到喂咕咕<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aqf3t75k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faqf3t75k&h=dcb28dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離開神社之後就繼續向前行<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yq7fldvh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyq7fldvh&h=63a5255f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾經辛苦終於嚟到佐賀城, 但係座城呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5uzdrifn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5uzdrifn&h=1510d133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n71kogfs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn71kogfs&h=cf57c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來佐賀城唔係一座城堡嚟, 佢只係一間比較大嘅屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ivy6atl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ivy6atl&h=cf2c2a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h1difam7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh1difam7&h=707b2171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/54qlortp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F54qlortp&h=f026d3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/exwb2980\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fexwb2980&h=4b041dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐賀城隔離仲有個歷史博物館同美術館, 不過小弟冇乜藝術細胞所以就冇行到入個美術館<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nvz04jl5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnvz04jl5&h=83276f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/neq8lhs9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fneq8lhs9&h=eb9a6930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r0nbtkeo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr0nbtkeo&h=74b782c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qvox8sud\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqvox8sud&h=5f3e25fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行曬之後一心諗住去食和牛, 但好多鋪頭淨係做晚市, 搵左好耐先揾到一間有午市, 點知行到去啱啱好過左last order, 最後走去左食漢堡飽, 都叫做食過佐賀牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/wh1Q73j0g5qWKwdgf3hRyXBqqVgczRrC/IMG-20170518-WA0010.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2Fwh1Q73j0g5qWKwdgf3hRyXBqqVgczRrC%2FIMG-20170518-WA0010.jpeg&h=9ef08029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完之後就搭火車出發去諫早, 仲見到好靚既海景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8hyaks7p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8hyaks7p&h=98079afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hnewxv70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhnewxv70&h=8068f18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去諫早既目的就係為左睇一場普通嘅J League乙組聯賽, 至於點解唔睇甲組而睇乙組, 係因為九洲嘅甲組得一隊而果隊咁啱係作客, 所以哩有睇住乙組過下癮<br />\n<br />\n早左去到諫早, 可以慢慢行去球場<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gyvm4in2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgyvm4in2&h=40f506ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於行到去球場<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o8ejhp6r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo8ejhp6r&h=471df02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ds9h1l04\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fds9h1l04&h=2743a2e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有吉祥物係到同人影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dwi69u0z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdwi69u0z&h=70ab9025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n球場入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/zN2EsFrtV6oAQcAvMTPf9Vi8ISoCZXLZ/P_20170517_173834_PN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2FzN2EsFrtV6oAQcAvMTPf9Vi8ISoCZXLZ%2FP_20170517_173834_PN.jpg&h=e6e29abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後主場球隊憑住兩球12碼羸2:1, 睇完之後要即刻仆返去火車站趕尾班火車番Hostel<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z5hxelp1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz5hxelp1&h=e9423b0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1ef535e4b689f9343c23bd88f0801a770751800","tid":263213,"uid":62040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T21:14:02.000Z","msg":"正皮 <br />\n咁樣既孤身旅行真係好自由自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未去過九洲，睇落好似好舒服，同東京大阪果種繁華感覺完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618b6148bfb5b70dad75e6ac04309c4ef8d40e1f","tid":263213,"uid":77635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T23:51:45.000Z","msg":"之前一個人都想去 但好似好悶 留名學野"},{"pid":"d2588bb2f43bae57ca5ff77dd0ead36ba4bc4099","tid":263213,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"7月頭都去<br />\n留名"},{"pid":"e6f8f2b31f2f2275d71bf895d08244c65142714c","tid":263213,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T01:09:20.000Z","msg":"6月尾去留名<br />\n想問下你住個間hostel 叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0daae3de4680e4141c1a2e53bc5c4696bb26a54","tid":263213,"uid":54715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"7月頭會獨遊<br />\n留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b921dfad7cfb8c15d19edd1e4612878220badc3","tid":263213,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前一個人都想去 但好似好悶 留名學野</blockquote><br />\n自己一個人靜靜地幾舒服<br />\n仲要日本好天時藍天居多， 個人都開心d"},{"pid":"a43393d8591223fdb33367836435f755413e95d6","tid":263213,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6月尾去留名<br />\n想問下你住個間hostel 叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSharely Style Hakata（哈卡塔莎莉品質酒店）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80411a17ff781f8733c34e51d1a66e850c788ab0","tid":263213,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"樓主本身識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同得當地人溝通到垃圾極有限"},{"pid":"e6a61b98910029ac0c8b9374b452946d5308cc92","tid":263213,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主本身識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同得當地人溝通到垃圾極有限</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都係識聽同講下啲單字, 再加小小身體語言同估下佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5825d924fedb1afaae0036af31e3ae7ebfe147","tid":263213,"uid":62282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"Day 3 歴史公園 長崎<br />\n<br />\n因為住宿既問題又要再搭返火車去早諫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 不過今次就唔響早諫落直接搭到尾站長崎, 早一晚果陣plan去長崎稻佐山睇夜景, 所以就睇下條火車沿線有咩地方適合上晝去, 之後響Google map到見到有個好大既歴史公園就決定左去果到睇睇<br />\n<br />\n出左個車站之後見到既就係稻田, 稻田同埋稻田, 果刻心諗仆街究竟我去左乜野地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/updl3mvc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fupdl3mvc&h=79f1f24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lw29u7me\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flw29u7me&h=ea8d44be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左一陣之後終於見到個指示牌<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lypvfuz7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flypvfuz7&h=53ff2e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行左1km左右陣終於到個門口<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0vwfm123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0vwfm123&h=b9a5fe91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個歴史公園主要係模仿返彌生人時代嘅環境出嚟, 有護城河, 櫓, 圍牆等等嘅防守型建築物<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uq5c0znt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuq5c0znt&h=985f4536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/noz6le5a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnoz6le5a&h=0ef3ec6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mrtb4h0a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmrtb4h0a&h=38ab9de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來當時嘅人平均身高得163cm, 睇黎我都可能係佢地嘅後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j60eg8vw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj60eg8vw&h=b3082ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錢人就可以著靚衫, 窮撚淨係可以著麻布<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/scfhwv34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fscfhwv34&h=e8fd678e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣時嘅居住環境, 都大過香港啲劏房好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8o36gb0l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8o36gb0l&h=c9417db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/guzpe1mh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fguzpe1mh&h=dd2ccc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣已經有巫女出現, 用一啲儀式去召喚番歷代君主嘅亡魂<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/67aoxfbl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F67aoxfbl&h=6fed2385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去睇墳墓, 一個個凸出黎嘅就係墳墓<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v1cwjrio\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv1cwjrio&h=38701ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/5ScRdZHEo8R3rVOlfteuMdt8umo2nF4H/DSC_0189.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2F5ScRdZHEo8R3rVOlfteuMdt8umo2nF4H%2FDSC_0189.JPG&h=2fbc47e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷念爺爺系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/75m4upet\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F75m4upet&h=d73b13da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇個guide話穿過左個森林就會有個另一個手作館, 響個森林到兜左好耐先發現原來有捷徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mc0i7je6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmc0i7je6&h=f4daf558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無雙入面個卑彌呼<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ntq34sp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ntq34sp&h=e58f744a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢有接駁巴士可以搭番去入口果到, 但係我就廢事等諗住行番出去, 點知一行就行左半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xnl9e6sa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxnl9e6sa&h=69b932ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dl2.pushbulletusercontent.com/CqWhhM1j9dH8X1qxKTbCdoaep2xripog/DSC_0210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdl2.pushbulletusercontent.com%2FCqWhhM1j9dH8X1qxKTbCdoaep2xripog%2FDSC_0210.JPG&h=dc97df59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有風但真係好好好曬, 終於有個地方消消暑<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k483edl9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk483edl9&h=e3aa04f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係搭火車果陣見到原來過幾日有個花火祭, 於是就即刻搵果個地方既交通同住宿, 20號啲酒店全部full曬, 好睇21號仲有1間酒店有房, 於是諗都冇諗就即刻book左佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6oanqwg4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6oanqwg4&h=92cfd977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到長崎都係睇和平公園, 原爆博物館, 一本鳥居, 同埋啲二戰遺跡<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s2cv4ih0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs2cv4ih0&h=da4f5a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kd9t4jb6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkd9t4jb6&h=3666704e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uznx5sa8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuznx5sa8&h=97cc422c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r2j70fm8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr2j70fm8&h=5a18c038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ya9nvlc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ya9nvlc&h=9c5ceb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/azij14vc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fazij14vc&h=fbc2730c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到柴犬係到玩水<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eip3b98l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feip3b98l&h=dc8b3028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原爆博物館<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2m0ijyor\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2m0ijyor&h=98d3c380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/50t1j3sx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F50t1j3sx&h=9cd1d26e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q4r3pmds\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq4r3pmds&h=327f001a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一本鳥居<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/087d6nij\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F087d6nij&h=80ad7465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7m2nubde\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7m2nubde&h=8f2e0e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長崎嘅電車<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2lmf69st\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2lmf69st&h=467ab0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住去睇個大教堂但去到已經close左, 唯有轉戰教堂後而嘅garden點知上到去就啱啱截左唔比入場, 最後淨係可以響個停車場到望下海<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6zbuyjae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6zbuyjae&h=3b424026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kbxqoec0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkbxqoec0&h=72fe60dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dkv581o3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdkv581o3&h=de2e7763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左個長崎和牛嘅包食<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d7hjox2f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd7hjox2f&h=6777115b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襯住仲有啲啲時間, 就睇多幾個舊式建築物<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jvcrd6h1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjvcrd6h1&h=7a5e3d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/plstj4r0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fplstj4r0&h=e33fc99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g5hkbdfy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg5hkbdfy&h=e6e02a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n響google map見到附近有個海岸公園, 於是就想去睇下係乜野樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f9n1koi5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff9n1koi5&h=26634695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e5syo1t4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe5syo1t4&h=e04dc5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a8p3u0h4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa8p3u0h4&h=8958b5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lr1nyim7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flr1nyim7&h=faea8d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個公園都幾relax, 有人係到釣魚,  有人係到放狗, 仲有好多中學生係到吹水係到玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ujbevrf4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fujbevrf4&h=f7a1cbc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gf6oep3s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgf6oep3s&h=48b75d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2uamgn0p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2uamgn0p&h=22879a21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fc03b9684e7c2db9559e7b6e8f24257e0f9fbf0","tid":263213,"uid":62282